Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:39.70,倒數,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(0,0,255,0,0,0000,1000)}{\t(0,0,1,\fscx200\fscy200)}4
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:40.75,倒數,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(0,0,255,0,0,0000,1000)}{\t(0,0,1,\fscx200\fscy200)}3
